00:45:49,592 --> 00:45:51,992
You know what?
That's really sneaky of you, Sara.

679
00:45:52,061 --> 00:45:54,325
- I'm not a bloody psychic.
- Eve, wait!

680
00:45:54,397 --> 00:45:56,365
Wait!

681
00:45:58,167 --> 00:46:01,000
- Eve. Eve!
