00:48:45,268 --> 00:48:49,068
- You guys want the tenant
on record in 1994?
- December, to be exact.

728
00:48:54,110 --> 00:48:57,341
- There's your tenant.
- Sebastian Mig-non?

729
00:48:57,413 --> 00:48:59,278
No. Mignon.
It's French.

730
00:48:59,348 --> 00:49:03,512
No, we're looking
for someone named Sara.
You got the right one?

731
00:49:03,586 --> 00:49:07,283
- Maybe he was her boyfriend.
- Thanks.

732
00:49:07,356 --> 00:49:11,224
- You did the right thing.
